data.text: @City_Press As a mother of two kids I have battled alot with my financial state to the point of begging from friends just to survive,until I started Bitcoin trading with the help of @_AMBREYMARCUS1 I made a successful withdrawal of R 200,000 with the help of @_ambreymarcus1.

@City_Press Being the head of the home isn't easy, you are expected to provide for the home, I lost my job during the pandemic and relied on the little money I had,things were hard until I met @_ambreymarcus1 and started Bitcoin trading, I earned  R150,000 in 3 weeks thanks @_ambreymarcus1.
